2. Visualizing the Multi-Stage Pipeline Execution
Because you configured needs: run_python_script and needs: check_aws_ssm, GitHub Actions visualizes and executes your pipeline as a strict sequential chain. Each stage spins up a completely separate, isolated ubuntu-latest virtual machine.

